Shomang, Simmonds and Tshazibana Are Appointed to South African Treasury

-- B y   M i k e   C o h e n
-- 
2011-06-23T08:28:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-23/shomang-simmonds-and-tshazibana-are-appointed-to-south-african-treasury.html
South Africa  apppointed Matthew
Simmonds as deputy director-general in the budget office of the
National Treasury and Nomfundo Tshazibana as deputy director-
general of economic policy analysis in the same department.  Samuel Shomang was named as deputy director-general of
asset and liability management at the Treasury, while Yasmin
Forbes and Nishi Choubey were appointed as non-executive
directors of the state-owned transportation company Transnet SOC
Ltd.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mike Cohen in Cape Town at 
 mcohen21@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Philip Sanders at 
 psanders@bloomberg.net  